    "content": "<!-- AI-IMAGE: doctor-hero-bg | Doctor detail page hero. Clinical setting for the doctor portrait to sit against.\n       SEARCH KEYWORDS: dental office interior, clinical setting, operatory, professional dental environment.\n       REQUIREMENTS: Landscape, minimum 1920x800, professional quality.\n       FALLBACK: Any dental office or clinical setting photo.\n       INSTRUCTION: Replace ONLY the url() value inside the section's background-image style; keep the linear-gradient overlay intact. Do not render this as an <img> element. -->\n<section class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-doctor-hero relative w-full min-h-[560px] md:min-h-[680px] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden py-20 md:py-24 bg-center bg-cover bg-no-repeat text-ivory\" style=\"background-image:linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(15,23,42,0.75), rgba(15,23,42,0.55), rgba(15,23,42,0.85)), url('https://picsum.photos/1920/800?random=doctor');\"><div class=\"relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-6\"><span class=\"text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.18em] uppercase font-sans text-white/60\">Our Team</span></div><!-- AI-CONTENT: doctor-hero-heading | Replace \"Dr. Jane Smith\" with the actual doctor name. --><h1 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-doctor-hero-component-heading font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-white font-medium leading-[1.1] mb-6\">Meet <span class=\"text-accent\">Dr. Jane Smith</span></h1><!-- AI-CONTENT: doctor-hero-subtitle | Replace with a short tagline about the doctor. --><p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-doctor-hero-component-subtitle text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto font-sans text-white/90\">Dedicated to providing compassionate, high-quality dental care for every patient.</p></div></section>"
  },
  {
    "name": "section-doctor-bio",
    "content": "<section class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-doctor-bio bg-white py-16 md:py-24 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center\"><div><!-- AI-IMAGE: doctor-photo | Replace with professional headshot. Portrait orientation, min 600x800. --><img src=\"https://picsum.photos/600/800?random=drphoto\" alt=\"Dr. Jane Smith\" class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-doctor-bio-component-photo w-full rounded-3xl object-cover shadow-lg\" /></div><div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-5\"><div class=\"h-px w-8 bg-primary\"></div><span class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-doctor-bio-component-eyebrow text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.18em] uppercase font-sans text-primary\">About Dr. Smith</span></div><!-- AI-CONTENT: doctor-bio-heading | Replace with a heading about the doctor's approach. --><h2 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-doctor-bio-component-heading font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-gray-900 font-medium leading-[1.1] mb-6\">A passion for patient care</h2><!-- AI-CONTENT: doctor-bio-para-1 | Replace with doctor's personal mission and philosophy. 2-4 sentences, warm tone. --><p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-doctor-bio-component-para-1 text-gray-600 text-base leading-relaxed mb-4 font-sans\">Dr. Jane Smith brings over fifteen years of clinical experience to her practice, with a focus on making every patient feel comfortable and informed. She believes that a healthy smile starts with trust between doctor and patient, and she takes the time to listen to each person's concerns before recommending treatment.</p><!-- AI-CONTENT: doctor-bio-para-2 | Replace with doctor's background, education, and personal interests. 3-5 sentences. --><p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-doctor-bio-component-para-2 text-gray-600 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6 font-sans\">After earning her dental degree, Dr. Smith completed advanced training in restorative and cosmetic dentistry. She has spent years refining her techniques to deliver results that look natural and last. Outside the office, she enjoys hiking with her family, volunteering at local health clinics, and staying current with the latest advancements in dental technology.</p>\n<!-- AI-CONTENT: cta-label | Choose label by business.category:\n       - Endodontist / Endodontics → \"Book Appointment\"\n       - Orthodontist / Orthodontics → \"Schedule a Consultation\"\n       - Default / other dental → \"Request a Consultation\"\n       Apply the same label consistently across header, body, and footer CTAs for this site. -->\n<a href=\"/consultation\" class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-doctor-bio-component-cta inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary text-white px-7 py-4 rounded-full font-medium text-base transition-opacity hover:opacity-90 font-sans\">Schedule with Dr. Smith</a></div></div></section>"
  },
